      "content": "it's hard to hear you say that... but it's also the only thing that makes sense. i feel like i'm just watching them struggle because of me. if i just wasn't around anymore, they wouldn't have to carry me. is it... is it actually okay to feel this way? to think that leaving might be the kindest thing i can do?",
